      "duration": 1.92,
      "size": 30672,
      "text": "地图上那一圈圈的等高线，是怎么从高度数据里画出来的？"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "marching-squares",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-2",
      "filename": "intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/marching-squares/yunxi/intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.02,
      "size": 32256,
      "text": "我们手里只有一张离散的数值网格，每个格点记录一个高度。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "marching-squares",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-3",
      "filename": "intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/marching-squares/yunxi/intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.04,
      "size": 32688,
      "text": "行进方块算法，就能把这些散点连成平滑的等高线。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "marching-squares",
      "section_id": "sample",
      "line_id": "def-1",
      "filename": "sample-def-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/marching-squares/yunxi/sample-def-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.07,
      "size": 33120,
      "text": "先把整个区域切成一个个小方格，这就是标量场网格。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "marching-squares",
      "section_id": "sample",
      "line_id": "def-2",
      "filename": "sample-def-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/marching-squares/yunxi/sample-def-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.61,
      "size": 25776,
      "text": "每个格点的值，可以想成那一点的海拔高度。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "marching-squares",
      "section_id": "sample",
      "line_id": "def-3",
      "filename": "sample-def-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/marching-squares/yunxi/sample-def-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.25,
      "size": 36000,
      "text": "我们设定一个阈值，比如海拔一千米，要画出这条高度线。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "marching-squares",
      "section_id": "lookup",
      "line_id": "case-1",
      "filename": "lookup-case-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/marching-squares/yunxi/lookup-case-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.82,
      "size": 29088,
      "text": "看每个方格的四个角，比阈值高记作一，低记作零。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "marching-squares",
      "section_id": "lookup",
      "line_id": "case-2",
      "filename": "lookup-case-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/marching-squares/yunxi/lookup-case-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.02,
      "size": 32400,
      "text": "四个角各是零或一，一共有二的四次方，也就是十六种组合。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "marching-squares",
      "section_id": "interaction",
      "line_id": "int-1",
      "filename": "interaction-int-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/marching-squares/yunxi/interaction-int-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.85,
      "size": 29664,
      "text": "拖动阈值滑块，看等高线随高度层层收缩。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "marching-squares",
      "section_id": "interaction",
      "line_id": "int-2",
