      "path": "audio/narrations/marching-squares/yunxi/interaction-int-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.38,
      "size": 38016,
      "text": "阈值越高，曲线越贴近山峰，把两座高斯峰勾勒得清清楚楚。"
    },
    {
